videos.headline: Purdue ties it up on 62-yard TD
videos.description: Purdue QB David Blough connects with WR Gregory Phillips for a 62-yard touchdown to tie the game against Bowling Green at 28.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Purdue ties it up on 62-yard TD) 2015/09/26 ESHEET

videos.headline: Bowling Green RB will not be denied for game-winning TD
videos.description: Bowling Green running back Travis Greene rushes 12 yards for a game-winning touchdown with nine seconds left in the the fourth quarter against Purdue.
